Oronwen is the owner of Lletya Seamstress. Her shop sells needles, thread, balls of wool and six colours of dye. She can repair a torn pair of mourner trousers in exchange for two pieces of silk and a piece of bear fur.

Treasure Trails[edit | edit source]

Oronwen is the solution to the elite anagram clue: NO OWNER. The answer to her question is 20.
